      <title>币安必须在美国面临因加密货币损失而重新提起的投资者诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-must-face-revived-investor-lawsuit-us-over-crypto-losses-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，联邦上诉法院重新启动了一项诉讼，投资者指控全球最大的加密货币交易所币安违反美国证券法，出售未注册的代币，导致其价值大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-must-face-revived-investor-lawsuit-us-over-crypto-losses-2024-03-08/</guid>
